'''Gall City''', also known as '''Gall Spaceport''', was an [[Imperial-class spaceport]] catering to civilian, corporate, and [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial Military]] needs on the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Gall/Legends|Gall]]. The nearby [[Cadavine Sector Fleet Imperial Enclave]] protected the starport.

[[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] utilized the area while being pursued by [[Dash Rendar/Legends|Dash Rendar]]. Other mercenaries, particularly [[IG-88D/Legends|IG-88D]], were also involved in the chase. It was here that Boba Fett demonstrated that the [[Slave I/Legends|''Slave I'']] could be operated remotely.

